<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David, the servant of Yahweh, when he sang to Yahweh the words of this song onthe day that Yahweh rescued him from the hand of all his enemies and from the hand of Saul. He sang:</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />I love you, Yahweh, my strength.</para>
